<plot>A true story of Esther, a grandmother that a grandchild never met. A paternal mother who died when her father was 8 years old.  The only few people left to talk about Ester would comment to the granddaughter on the uncanny resemblance between them. This resemblance inspired the granddaughter to fly to Guadalajara, Mexico, to meet some of Ester's family and discover more about her life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?182467</url></doc>
